{"tid":1161013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正經post回帶】睇時勢歸邊嘅人係咪真係叻？回顧蘇聯時期useful idiots嘅下場","createTime":"2019-05-19T00:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T17:48:13.000Z","uid":131691,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2c741134e5ef0f7bf31da5410b752423a4a31b33","tid":1161013,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T00:18:31.000Z","msg":"舊post archive：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/16o5Xc_t72HBHhFC0ewfPsVQ9NAvknPUR?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F16o5Xc_t72HBHhFC0ewfPsVQ9NAvknPUR%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=aa566305\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/16o5Xc_t72HBHhFC0ewfPsVQ9NAvknPUR?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">內裏有舊post嘅Google Doc（共產顛覆手法，老鼠天堂，終止思想嘅諺語，等等），RedDragon1會員嘅詳盡Yuri Bechmenov「顛覆過程」新翻譯，仲有卷殘會員嘅Edward Griffin與Yuri Bezmenov interview嘅翻譯</span><br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL;DR: 背靠牆壁，排成一行，槍決。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/125438_a6930e81c1ed6c6f95ee2a7aa915fcf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F125438_a6930e81c1ed6c6f95ee2a7aa915fcf8.jpg&h=094f94e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當一個共產政權想入侵一個地方嘅時候，都會先用計「顛覆」subvert當地社會，其中一個方法就係招攬當地人去投靠外來嘅政權，喺當地宣揚共產入侵者嘅好。冷戰時期，蘇聯嘅顛覆手法被一班叛變嘅特工流出。以下係取自Yuri Bezmenov同G. Edward Griffin嘅訪問。首先係source，跟住係主文。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">===Source===</span><br />\n卷殘巴打中文翻譯訪問全文：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/11b-0RiEaSKMRyRaU2PZpmRlzVMp9D3KBTOezezQ61bw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F11b-0RiEaSKMRyRaU2PZpmRlzVMp9D3KBTOezezQ61bw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=6e5b0152\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/11b-0RiEaSKMRyRaU2PZpmRlzVMp9D3KBTOezezQ61bw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n英文transcript：<a href=\"https://uselessdissident.blogspot.com/2008/11/interview-with-yuri-bezmenov-part-three.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuselessdissident.blogspot.com%2F2008%2F11%2Finterview-with-yuri-bezmenov-part-three.html&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=788625ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://uselessdissident.blogspot.com/2008/11/interview-with-yuri-bezmenov-part-three.html</a><br />\n訪問影片（個半鐘）：<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3qkf3bajd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy3qkf3bajd4&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=ffd99bf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y3qkf3bajd4</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">===主文===</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">共產式顛覆，吸引到會投靠嘅人不外有三：</span><br />\n1，一班真心想「真正共產主義」實現嘅學者/記者（理想派）<br />\n2，一班想幫手奪權後分一杯羹，坐享其成嘅有權/有錢人（現實派）<br />\n3，一班想打倒現有迂腐嘅學生/退休人士/無產階級（大洗牌派）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n好可惜，三者喺入侵政權嘅眼中，都係「有利用價值嘅白癡」，&ldquo;Useful idiots&rdquo;，因爲佢哋所知嘅嘢都係只有部份，利用價值亦只係短暫。</span><br />\n<br />\n對(1)，蘇聯嘅做法係邀請佢哋出席一啲華麗嘅官方場合，晚會，或學術研討會，目的係令到呢班理想派覺得共產政權=歌舞昇平，而且暗示共產黨執政後，佢哋就可以無止境咁喺呢啲華麗嘅場合發表觀點。返到自己國家，呢班人就會開始吹奏敵國嘅繁榮。<span style=\"color: red;\">對(1)發放嘅虛假願景，就係「真正共產執政係完美」。</span><br />\n<br />\n對(2)，蘇聯嘅做法係提供經濟甜頭，發展機會，目的係令到呢班現實派覺得投靠外來政權就係賺錢唯一方法，背棄自己族羣嘅利益，賺咗先算，有錢之後仲會喺共產執政嘅世界分一杯羹，做寨主。返到自己國家，呢班人就會開始將利益輸送畀外來政權。<span style=\"color: red;\">對(2)發放嘅虛假願景，就係「投靠共產政權就發達」。</span><br />\n<br />\n對(3)，蘇聯嘅做法係提供發泄渠道，簡單化之後矛頭指向一個人或者一件事，將佢哋嘅自卑化爲社會撕裂，並推出「共產執政=社會和諧」作爲solution。呢個情況放喺香港，就係衍生出「廢老vs廢青vs藍絲vs黃絲」呢啲撕裂假象。返到自己國家，呢班人就會開始幫外來政權去「維穩」，批鬥一啲反抗外來政權嘅人。<span style=\"color: red;\">對(3)發放嘅虛假願景，就係「共產政權=和諧」。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n好可惜，歷史話畀我哋聽，呢三班人如果決定投共，係冇一個有好下場。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據Yuri Bezmenov：<br />\n新德里左翼理想主義記者，被處決。<br />\n河內親共嘅useful idiots，被處決。<br />\n尼加拉瓜，馬克思主義者入獄。<br />\n格林納達，馬克思主義者Maurice Bishop被另一位新馬克思主義者處決。<br />\n阿富汗，首先是Nur Muhammad Taraki，被Hafizullah Amin殺死，然後Amin在KGB的協助下被Babrak Karmal殺死。<br />\n孟加拉，Sheikh Mujibur Rahman，一位非常親蘇聯的左翼分子，被他自己的馬克思列寧主義軍隊中的同僚暗殺。<br />\n與蘇聯合作的大多數印度人，特別是與蘇聯大使館信息部合作的，都被列入處決名單。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在他們的任務完成的那一刻，所有這些有利用價值的白痴要麼完全被處決，要麼被流放，或者仿傚古巴那般入獄。</span><br />\n<br />\n===================================<br />\n<br />\n<strong>究竟舐共，「識時務投靠共產黨」，係咪真係咁多人所講嘅「精」呢？<br />\n你幫中共賺嘅錢，係咪真係屬於你嘅呢？<br />\n你幫中共奪嘅權，係咪真係屬於你嘅呢？<br />\n你諗住做順民，係咪真係會安全呢？<br />\n你諗住移民之後就無事，又係咪真係嘅呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n退休多年嘅前蘇聯特工，喺英國被俄羅斯落毒：<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/topics/c0j915myy8kt/russian-spy-poisoning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftopics%2Fc0j915myy8kt%2Frussian-spy-poisoning&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=32bc41a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftopics%2Fc0j915myy8kt%2Frussian-spy-poisoning&h=8fb23d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/topics/c0j915myy8kt/russian-spy-poisoning</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共真正嚟到香港，舐共嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">下場</span>，又會係點呢？</span>"},{"pid":"5326a098b72ddba69f598b42854c0c2528845639","tid":1161013,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T00:23:16.000Z","msg":"所以資歷有咁上下嘅石禮謙都唔敢歸邊"},{"pid":"30250a7f089b7ba6eba4bfb8481aa3e2141e58e8","tid":1161013,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T00:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21ec2acb8beb7fa668c65d7cd99a95db8cdb3a7","tid":1161013,"uid":82640,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"5326a098b72ddba69f598b42854c0c2528845639","tid":1161013,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"rep